ComicInfo.Title: What Power Unleashed?
ComicInfo.Summary: What Power Unleashed?: The Silver Surfer defeats Duroc by taking him to the far future and leaving him on a desolated planet Earth. Meanwhile, Thor attempts to liberate Asgard from the tyranny of Loki. He fails. Loki sentences him to death.
